      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has started to soften, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>beef stock mix</strong> to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Return the <strong>browned meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>pork & beef meatballs with tomato sauce</strong></p>",
